      • PATTERN_COMPILE

        public static final org.objectweb.asm.commons.Method PATTERN_COMPILE
        A Method instance for Pattern.compile(java.lang.String). This isn't available from Definition because we intentionally don't add it there so that the script can't create regexes without this syntax. Essentially, our static regex syntax has a monopoly on building regexes because it can do it statically. This is both faster and prevents the script from doing something super slow like building a regex per time it is run.
